snippet.title: Crawler - More animations and refined textures
snippet.description:
The Crawler creature I sculpted, retopologised and textured for Helios Games' PC title Pavor. I made a simple rig and some fairly quick animations to test it out, the game will be quite different. 
https://discord.gg/a24VBkS

I did all work, concept by Jedi Roman, https://www.artstation.com/artwork/vK1b6https://www.artstation.com/artwork/vK1b6

Zbrush/Maya/Substance Painter/Marmoset Toolbag
